{"tid":349983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報道指金管局向銀行收集中國銀聯卡提款數據","createTime":"2017-08-07T02:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T02:42:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c8d1e29f6e5a6cfa71d9b6964e5b3075288ab7c","tid":349983,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"據《蘋果日報》報道，金管局要求銀行提供上半年內地銀聯卡ATM機提款數據；報道指，金管局上周向港銀行發出通知，要求收集今年首6個月內地銀聯卡戶經行方旗下ATM，提款宗數及金額累計資料，是該局首次收集相關數據，業界需本週匯報。<br />\n<br />\n金管局回應指，會與銀行就不同議題不時溝通，不評論溝通的具體內容。<br />\n<br />\n銀行界估計，當局或基於宏觀風險管理，先收集相關數據再作分析，未必一定是為採用澳門做法而鋪路，除非有證據顯示本港洗錢問題嚴峻，否則如要在ATM安裝視像鏡頭或身份證讀卡器，以進行雙重認證，必然招致業界強烈反彈。<br />\n<br />\n澳門金融管理局在上月初突然宣布，對未安裝「認識你的客戶」(KYC)技術的自動櫃員機，停止內地銀聯銀行卡的提款服務，即是內地客須通過身份證和容貌雙重認證才可在櫃員機提款。"},{"pid":"924671c79fa457c3534a92cc08b8ec42a400cb17","tid":349983,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:23:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1502071379899&amp;issue=20170807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1502071379899%26issue%3D20170807&d=DWHvdOTzsFEJLSLEGP%2BqUZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3d7f39d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1502071379899%26issue%3D20170807&h=f6dee7fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1502071379899&amp;issue=20170807</a>"},{"pid":"33a93c264dee0b3504aab17620fd25c9b6fdda73","tid":349983,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:26:12.000Z","msg":"依排做好多小動作喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdf7867e7742b7dbf466ac2e80b463aee97b4ed","tid":349983,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T02:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e018a57339f789b29224f5e00120e699e59311d","tid":349983,"uid":10757,"like":0,"